    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes an approach for Resource Public Key
   Infrastructure (RPKI) Relying Parties to detect a particular form of
   RPKI Repository Delta Protocol (RRDP) session desynchronization and
   how to recover, as implemented in OpenBSD's rpki-client validator.</t>
